import React from 'react'
import { Box, Stack, CircularProgress} from '@mui/material'

const Loader = () => (
        <Box minHeight='95vh'>
            <Stack direction='row' justifyContent='center' alignItems='center' height='80vh'>
                <CircularProgress />
            </Stack>
        </Box>
    )


export default Loader
